---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Partner - Investors">
  <Navigation />
  <main>
    <section class="partner-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>partner with us: investors</h1>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="investors-partner">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="partner-content">
          <h2>why partner with the tech bros</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">We introduce investors to exceptional technical founders early.</p>
          <p>Our community includes women building in AI, robotics, biotech, climate, and deep tech, many of whom are pre-incorporation or pre-raise. These are founders you won't meet through warm intros or demo days.</p>
          
          <h3>partnering with us allows you to:</h3>
          <ul class="partner-list">
            <li>Build relationships before rounds are competitive</li>
            <li>Be top of mind for high-potential technical founders</li>
            <li>Develop genuine founder trust outside a pitch context</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>what partnership looks like</h2>
          <p>You sponsor an event designed to bring you into the room early, not on a stage at the end.</p>
          
          <h3>formats include:</h3>
          <ul class="partner-list">
            <li>Founderâ€“investor salons</li>
            <li>Panels with portfolio founders</li>
            <li>Small-group discussions and working sessions</li>
          </ul>
          <p>We prioritise depth, not deal theatre.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="spotlight-hero-image">
      <img src="/partner/mercuri-canva-event-hero.jpg" alt="Mercuri Ventures x Canva Event" />
    </div>

    <section class="spotlight-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="spotlight-content">
          <div class="spotlight-images-left">
            <img src="/partner/mercuri-canva-1.jpg" alt="Mercuri Ventures x Canva Event" />
            <img src="/partner/mercuri-canva-2.jpg" alt="Mercuri Ventures x Canva Event" />
            <img src="/partner/mercuri-canva-3.jpg" alt="Mercuri Ventures x Canva Event" />
          </div>
          <div class="spotlight-text-column">
            <h2>spotlight: mercuri ventures x canva</h2>
            <p>We partnered with Mercuri Ventures and Canva on a hackathon connecting technical women with experienced operators and investors.</p>
            <div class="spotlight-stats">
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">35</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">participants</div>
              </div>
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">80%</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">in target fields (CS / AI / Maths / Engineering / Robotics)</div>
              </div>
              <div class="spotlight-stat">
                <div class="spotlight-number">4.5</div>
                <div class="spotlight-label">stars</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Multiple YC founders on the panel</p>
            <p>Founders cited the quality of discussion and transparency as standout, and many continued conversations well beyond the event.</p>
            
            <div class="spotlight-quotes">
              <blockquote>Today has been great! I loved the collaborative effort of everyone and getting us to actual problem solve!</blockquote>
              <blockquote>It's been a lovely event to brainstorm and network! I definitely feel even more inspired to become a founder in future, knowing I have a solid foundation for that. Thank you once again for the event ðŸ’ž</blockquote>
              <blockquote>I had so much fun! I thought the set up was amazing and I really appreciated the panel in the morning. The whole experience has definitely improved my confidence and the panel made me really excited about the idea to found or co-found my own startup. I would love to attend future events!</blockquote>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="investors-partner">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="partner-content">

          <div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <a href="mailto:team@thetechbros.io" class="btn">Connect With Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .partner-hero {
    padding: 6rem 0 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .investors-partner {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .partner-content {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .partner-content h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
  }

  .partner-content h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .partner-content h3 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .partner-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .partner-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .partner-list li {
    padding: 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .partner-list li::before {
    content: 'â†’';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .spotlight-hero-image {
    width: 100%;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .spotlight-hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .spotlight-section {
    padding: 4rem 0;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .spotlight-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .spotlight-images-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .spotlight-images-left img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .spotlight-text-column h2 {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .spotlight-quotes {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .spotlight-quotes blockquote {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .spotlight-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
  }

  .spotlight-stat {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .spotlight-number {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(239, 31, 159, 0.5);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .spotlight-label {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .spotlight-stats {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .spotlight-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .spotlight-text-column {
      order: 1;
    }

    .spotlight-images-left {
      order: 2;
    }
  }
</style>
